	or 8 insns.
	(ppc_elf_link_hash_table_create): Init new ppc_elf_params field.
	(allocate_dynrelocs): Use new GLINK_ENTRY_SIZE.
	(ppc_elf_size_dynamic_sections): Likewise.  Size branch table
	by PLT reloc count.
